'''Kannoth''' was an [[eladrin]] [[archfey]] [[vampire lord]] who ruled over [[Cendriane]] in the [[Feywild]].{{Cite dragon/391/Watchers at the Living Gate|67}}

He was described as a man of middle height, dark, delicate and slender, and dressed in a jacket of wine-colored velvet. He carried a lily at the end of a long stalk as a weapon.{{Cite dragon/391/Watchers at the Living Gate|67}}

It was said that he had an army of undead soldiers who worshipped him as a god.{{Cite dragon/391/Watchers at the Living Gate|67}} Alternatively, that he was the master of a bloodthirsty cult lurking beneath the earth.
